            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A sceaduinar is treated as an undead creature for the purposes of spells, abilities, and effects that heal, deal damage to, or bypass the resistances of an undead creature. Similarly, a sceaduinar is treated as an unliving creature for spells, abilities, and effects that heal living creatures.",
