                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Sceaduinars are immune to effects that target souls (such as a soul upload trap) or require knowledge of a creature\u2019s identity (such as scrying). When slain, they can\u2019t be restored to life by magic except by a miracle or wish, or by divine intervention.",
